00:38:42.539 --> 00:38:44.160
[Meryl} Excellent, excellent question.

00:38:44.720 --> 00:38:52.080
I always recommend closed captions, because 
it puts the viewer in control. For example, if I

00:38:52.080 --> 00:38:58.720
don't like the font that they're showing I can 
change it with closed captions. With open captions

00:38:58.720 --> 00:39:06.160
you can't turn them off and on. You can't, if 
if they're terrible, you can't fix it. It affects

00:39:06.160 --> 00:39:13.200
