00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:23.440
because LinkedIn has lost the caption file on some 
of my videos. And for me that's worse than viewer

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:30.720
control, because I cannot have any of my videos not 
have captions because I want to walk your talk. So

00:39:31.280 --> 00:39:37.120
closed captioning is my first recommendation,
because it lets the viewer control the caption.

